column5: Has or is anyone fishing Kabinakagami Lake this year? If you have how did you do. Going in late July. Staying at Pine Portage Lodge. Any info would be appreciated. Thanks
Has or is anyone fishing Kabinakagami Lake this year? If you have how did you do. Going in late July. Staying at Pine Portage Lodge. Any info would be appreciated. Thanks
Leaving for Kaby 7/2. Also staying at PPL. This will be our 9th year.I'll update you on return.

Fished out of Pine Portage the end of May. Did real good again this year. Three of us fished five days and had a total of 303 walleyes and 46 pike. Almost all of the fish were within the slot limit. Never fished the lake later than the second week of June and always have had good luck.
